### GameBuddy API Tests
### Base URL for local development
@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001

###

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Get All Kids
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids

###

### Get Kid Profile - Alex
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/profile

###

### Get Kid Profile - Mila
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/mila/profile

###

### Get Kid Profile - Sam
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/sam/profile

###

### Get Kid Profile - Unknown Kid (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/unknown/profile

###

### Get Kid Preferences - Alex
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/preferences

###

### Get Kid Preferences - Mila
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/mila/preferences

###

### Get Kid Preferences - Sam
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/sam/preferences

###

### Get Kid Preferences - Unknown Kid (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/unknown/preferences

###

### Get Kid Progress - Alex
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/progress

###

### Get Kid Progress - Mila
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/mila/progress

###

### Get Kid Progress - Sam
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/sam/progress

###

### Get Kid Progress - Unknown Kid (returns empty progress)
GET {{baseUrl}}/kids/unknown/progress

###

### Get All Kids Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/all

###

### Record Quiz Completion - Alex (Single Country)
POST {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/quiz-completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "countriesCovered": ["France"],
  "correctAnswers": 1,
  "totalQuestions": 1
}

###

### Record Quiz Completion - Alex (Multiple Countries)
POST {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/quiz-completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "countriesCovered": ["Germany", "Italy", "Spain"],
  "correctAnswers": 2,
  "totalQuestions": 3
}

###

### Record Quiz Completion - Mila (5 countries quiz)
POST {{baseUrl}}/kids/mila/quiz-completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "countriesCovered": ["Canada", "Mexico", "Brazil", "Argentina", "Chile"],
  "correctAnswers": 4,
  "totalQuestions": 5
}

###

### Record Quiz Completion - Invalid (Non-existent kid)
POST {{baseUrl}}/kids/unknown/quiz-completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "countriesCovered": ["France"],
  "correctAnswers": 1,
  "totalQuestions": 1
}

###

### Record Quiz Completion - Invalid (Empty countries array)
POST {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/quiz-completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "countriesCovered": [],
  "correctAnswers": 1,
  "totalQuestions": 1
}

###

### Record Quiz Completion - Invalid (Correct answers exceeds total)
POST {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/quiz-completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "countriesCovered": ["France"],
  "correctAnswers": 5,
  "totalQuestions": 3
}

###

### Record Quiz Completion - Invalid (Negative correct answers)
POST {{baseUrl}}/kids/alex/quiz-completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "countriesCovered": ["France"],
  "correctAnswers": -1,
  "totalQuestions": 1
}

